arts.ttl: Colombia v Australia: men’s international football friendly – live
arts.sum: Updates as the Socceroos face Los Cafeteros at Citi Field Any thoughts? Get in touch with an email Unsurprisingly the support in Queens is overwhelming in favour of Colombia. Roughly 150,000 residents of the New York borough hail from the South American nation. The two sides make their way out onto the diamond, each group of players wearing 90s retro neon piped anthem jackets. They both line up in a very skew-whiff arrangement, in keeping with the odd dimensions of the playing arena. Continue reading...
